project-1:

1)
npm init
package name: (repo-mern-stack) ecommerce
entry point: (index.js) backend/server.js

2)
npm i express mongoose dotenv nodemon

3)package.json/scripts, add:
    "start": "node backend/server.js",
    "dev": "nodemon backend/server.js"

4)package.json, add:
"type": "module",
It'll allow import and export keyword.

5) 
npm i bcryptjs jsonwebtoken validator nodemailer cookie-parser body-parser


frontend:

1)
npm i axios react-helmet @reduxjs/toolkit react-redux redux redux-thunk react-router-dom overlay-navbar webfontloader react-icons react-rating-stars-component

2)
npm i react-alert react-alert-template-basic redux-devtools-extension 